## Format Detection

The CLI determines input format from the file extension. This works for most cases:

| Extension | Format |
|:----------|:-------|
| `.xml` | XML |
| `.json` | JSON |
| `.yaml`, `.yml` | YAML |

Use `--as` to override detection for files with non-standard extensions.

